    <item>
      <title>南非部长计划进行彻底变革以结束水危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/south-africa-water-municipalities-to-cede-water-provision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非水务部长森佐·姆楚努 (Senzo Mchunu) 计划彻底改革国家水务行业，并免除市政当局的供水责任，因为距离全国选举还有两个月，供水中断激怒了公民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/south-africa-water-municipalities-to-cede-water-provision</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:06:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴尔的摩希望以每栋 1 美元的价格出售数百套空置房屋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/baltimore-wants-to-sell-hundreds-of-vacant-homes-for-1-each</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴尔的摩官员正在决定是否以 1 美元的象征性价格出售用木板封起来的房屋，以吸引房主对饱受犯罪和年久失修困扰的社区进行修缮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/baltimore-wants-to-sell-hundreds-of-vacant-homes-for-1-each</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰总理预计美国最早将于本月提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/ukrainian-premier-sees-us-aid-coming-as-early-as-this-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总理表示，美国受阻的资金最早可能在本月到达，而且为前线招募新兵的规模可能少于军方最初支持的 50 万人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/ukrainian-premier-sees-us-aid-coming-as-early-as-this-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛哈祖斯称通胀走低，六月可能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/goldman-s-hatzius-says-inflation-headed-lower-june-cut-likely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团首席经济学家 Jan Hatzius 表示，尽管近几个月公布的数据较高，但美国通胀仍处于下行通道，支持该行 6 月份降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/goldman-s-hatzius-says-inflation-headed-lower-june-cut-likely</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
